label: A2B3C12D12_cI232_230_a_c_h_h-001
title: Ca$_{3}$Al$_{2}$(OH)$_{12}$ ($J2_{3}$) Structure
comments: The original determination of this structure by (Brandenberger, 1933) did not locate the hydrogen atoms, and according to (Gottfried, 1937) used the coordinates of \href{current_web_home_dir/A2B3C12D3_cI160_230_a_c_h_d-001}{garnet, $S1_{4}$}.  (Bartl, 1986) was able to locate the hydrogen atoms, and as they do not change the space group we include them in the $J2_{3}$ structure.
